<h2 id="4.12">HIVE SDK v4.12</h2>
[av_toggle_container mode='toggle' initial='0']
[av_toggle title="HIVE SDK v4.12.0"]
[markdown]

* Released: 2019-Sep-04

##### New Features

* None

##### Changed Features
[/markdown]

<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]

* [IAP v4] Supported to use the Google Play Billing Library 2.0. 
   * Available to show discount prices.
      * Available to show original prices by using displayOriginalPrice and originalPrice field of IAPV4Product.
      * Available to check image URL by using iconURL field of IAPV4Product after setting icon image of each item.
   * Automatically refunded if the result of implementing `TransactionFinish()` method in the **IAPV4** class is not success within three days.
   * Added pending state to the result of implementing `purchase()` method in the **IAPV4** class.[/markdown]</li></ul>

[markdown]
##### Bug Fixes

* None [/markdown]
&nbsp;
<hr class="guide_line_1" />
[markdown]
##### Version of third-party Libraries for HIVE SDK v4.12.0

* Facebook SDK (Android) v4.39.0
* Facebook SDK (iOS) v4.39.1
* Firebase Library (Android) v15.0.1+
* GooglePlay Services Game, Auth (Android) v15.0.1+
* Google Sign-In SDK (iOS) v4.1.2
* <span style="color: blue;">Google Play Billing (Android) v2.0.0</span>
* Android Support Library (Android) v27.0.1+

**IDP**

* QQ (Android) v2.0.2 (r5961)
* QQ (iOS) v1.0.0
* VK (Android) v1.6.9
* VK (iOS) v1.4.6
* WeChat (Android) v1.4.0
* WeChat (iOS) v1.7

**IAP**

* ONE Store (Android) v17.02.00
* ONE Store (Android) v16.05.00
* WeChat (Android) v1.4.0

**Push**

* Jpush (Android) v1.7.2

**Marketing Tracking Analytics**

* Adjust (Android) v4.14.0
* Adjust (iOS) v4.14.1
* Singular (Android) v7.4.2
* Singular (iOS) v8.4.2
[/markdown]
