[markdown]
### Release Notes

* Version: v4.11.4
* Date: 2019-Apr-17

##### New Features
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]

* [Provisioning] Added a popup which restricts the access from selected countries to game. <span style="font-size: 8pt;"><a href="../../develop/basics/#hive-flow">See more</a></span>
* [Provisioning] Added a feature named remote logging, which collects both HIVE log and game log by activating target user log. <span style="font-size: 8pt;"><a href="../../develop/authv4/initializing-hive/#remote-logging">See more</a></span> [/markdown]</li></ul>

[markdown]
##### Changed Features
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]

* [Provisioning] Updated the permission notice.
* [Provisioning] Expanded the range of using HIVE platform to new corporate. <span style="font-size: 8pt;"><a href="../../develop/authv4/terms/#new-corp">See more</a></span>
* [Promotion] Changed to allow promotion popup to configure YouTube configuration. <span style="font-size: 8pt;"><a href="../../operation/promotion/youtube">See more</a></span>
* [Auth v4/Auth v1] Changed the inquiry URL of customer service.
* [Marketing Attribution] Updated the version of Singular library in use.
   * Used version: [Android] v7.4.0, [iOS] v8.3.4
   * Updated version: [Android] v7.4.2, [iOS] v8.4.2
* [Analytics] Added codes to the part of game access to distinguish new user (NU) when sending furnnel logs. [/markdown]</li></ul>

<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]

* [Push] Changed to run the local push on the same process with game.  [/markdown]</li></ul>

<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel iOS">iOS</span>[markdown]

* [Push] Changed to use Provisional Authorization on devices with iOS 12 and later. <span style="font-size: 8pt;"><a href="../../develop/notification/#push-ios12">See more</a></span>
[/markdown]</li></ul>

[markdown]
##### Bug Fixes
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]

* [Auth v1/Auth v4] Changed to match the color of buttons on restriction popup regardless of OS. [/markdown]</li></ul>

<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]

* [Promotion] Fixed an error that keeps playing media files back on user device without screen lock. 
* [Auth v4/Auth v1] Fixed not to display permission notice UI when nothing left to notify.
* [Auth v1/Provisioning] Fixed not to deliver the download history whenever running your app.
* [Auth v1/Auth v4] Fixed to close the displayed popups such as access restriction popup, update popup, and server maintenance popup when user taps back button. [/markdown]</li></ul>

<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel iOS">iOS</span>[markdown]

* [Auth v4] Fixed an error that crashes on **hive_config.xml** file when the key named GoogleClientId has no value. [/markdown]</li></ul>

<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel unity">Unity</span>[markdown]

* Updated Gradle to the latest version to run on the latest version of Unity. [/markdown]</li></ul>


&nbsp;
