[markdown]
### Release Notes

* Version: v4.11.2
* Date: 2019-Jan-23

##### New Features
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]

* [Promotion] Added a sharing function, which was unavailable with one of default function, media transmission, while using User Acquisiton.  
   * Confirmed the running state on Facebook, LINE and KakaoTalk.
   * Added `share()` method to **PlatformHelper** class.
   * Added **PlatformShare** class.[/markdown]</li></ul>
[markdown]
##### Changed Features
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]

* [Push] Changed notification domain and its logic in accordance with the renewal of push notification.
   * Available to check whether user touched the received push.
* [Auth v1/Auth v4/Promotion] Changed to support various types of resolution for image resources in HIVE SDK.
   * Changed for permission notice, full banner and custom webview to support pad or tablet UI.
* [Auth v4] Changed to customize HIVE permission notice UI.
   * Added a function to deactivate permission notice UI.
   * Added a function to provide permission notice data.

* Updated the version of Facebo ok SDK in use. 
   * Used version: [Android/iOS] v4.38.0
   * Updated version: [Android] v4.39.0, [iOS] v4.39.1
* [COPPA] Added a function to control sending Facebook event and advertising identifier. [/markdown]</li></ul>

<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]

* [IAP v2/IAP v4] Changed Lebi domain. [/markdown]</li></ul>

[markdown]
##### Bug Fixes
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]

* [Unity/Plugin] Fixed the exceptional case occurred on Unity in case event handler is not unregistered. [/markdown]</li></ul>

<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]

* [Provisioning] Fixed an error that when the rest time on maintenance popup is more than 24 days, time format becomes negative number and popup closes in a second.
* [Push] Fixed not to crash on Firebase console when sending push notifications.
* [Provisioning] Fixed not to request the data-reading authority via SMS whenever user accesses app after user denied to allow reading data on user device. 
* [Unity/Plugin/Auth v4] Fixed to close soft keys displayed while signing in Google Play Games Services (PGS). [/markdown]</li></ul>

<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel iOS">iOS</span>[markdown]

* [Provisioning] Fixed to rotate permission notice popup.
* [CPP/Plugin/Provider/GameCenter] Fixed to progress acheivement after implementing `reportAchievement()` method.
* [Analytics] Fixed an error that in case `signIn()` method failed to log in, DID in transmitting analytics log is null when `setup()` method of  **AuthV4** class is initialized.
* [Auth v1] Fixed not to crash the activated COPPA on Authentication v1, which does not support COPPA.
* [Auth v4/Provisioning] Fixed not to crash on few devices which access from the country where terms of service is not displayed in case  game studio updates HIVE SDK earlier than v4.11.1. [/markdown]</li></ul>

&nbsp;
<hr class="guide_line_1" />
[markdown]
### <b>Hotfix Releases</b>
<br/>
#### v4.11.2.1

* Date: 2019-Feb-12

##### New Features
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]

* [AuthV4/ProviderGoogle] Added an API which returns the current state whether user signed in Google Play Games Services(PGS) or not.

   * Use `isConnected()` method of **ProviderGoogle** class.
* [AuthV4Helper] Supported achievement and leaderboard function of PGS with **AuthV4Helper** class. The function of PGS was available with **ProviderGoogle** class only.
   * Use `isConnected()` method of **ProviderGoogle** class. It works in accordance with the login status.

     | ProviderGoogle                      | AuthV4Helper                |
     | ----------------------------------- | --------------------------- |
     | ProviderGoogle.achievementsReveal() | Helper.achievementsReveal() |
     | ProviderGoogle.achievementsUnlock() | Helper.achievementsUnlock() |
     | ProviderGoogle.achievementsIncrement() | Helper.achievementsIncrement() |
     | ProviderGoogle.leaderboardsSubmitScore() | Helper.leaderboardsSubmitScore() |

[/markdown]</li></ul>
   [markdown]

##### Changed Features
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]

* [AuthV4Helper] Changed not to synchronize ID providers (IdP) prior to explicit login in case user cancelled implicit login to Google Play Games Services(PGS).
* [AuthV4Helper/ProviderGoogle] Changed to sign out the player account in case user who connected with Google Play Games Services (PGS) signed out from leaderboard or achievement view.
   * If user signed out on PGS UI from Google Provider-used game, it sends an error code, AuthV4GoogleLogout.
   * If user signed out on PGS UI from AuthV4Helper-used game, it sends an error code, AuthV4GoogleLogout, and signs out from AuthV4Helper.
 [/markdown]</li></ul>
[markdown]
##### Bug Fixes
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]

* [AuthV4Helper] Fixed not to activate implicit login again if user who did not connect with Google Play Games Services (PGS) signed out a game. [/markdown]</li></ul>

&nbsp;
