### Release Notes

* Version: v4.11.1
* Date: 2018-Nov-28

##### New Features

* None

##### Changed Features
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]

* [Provisioning] Changed not to request or use hardware identifiers.
* Changed not to request or send a MAC address of user device any more. [/markdown]</li></ul>
[markdown]
##### Bug Fixes
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]

* [AuthV4Helper] Fixed not to keep sign-in status after Google Play or Game Center failed synchronization while HIVE session is in use.
   * Occurred in the case of calling `signIn()` method of **AuthV4.Helper** class.
[/markdown]</li></ul>
