### Release Notes

- Version: v4.9.0
- Date: 2018-Jul-05

##### New Features
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]
- [Push] Added a feature which configures whether to display push mesasages (local push or remote push) or not while playing a game. <span style="font-size: 8pt;"><a href="../../develop/notification/#push-display-settings">See more</a></span>
- [Provisioning] Added numerous function buttons on a notice popup.
- [Analytics] Added a unique value (analytics_id) to identify values while analyzing data.
- [Auth v4] Added a popup feature which requests an agreement on collecting personal data as a response to the GDPR.
[/markdown]</li></ul>
[markdown]
##### Changed Features
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]
- [Analytics] Stopped supporting TUNE, a marketing attribution tool and relevant libraries.
- [Auth v1/Auth v4] Added the latest version of Facebook SDK and specified the feature handling expiry state of authentication tokens in accordance with changes in Facebook user access tokens policy. 
- [Auth v4] Changed to request essential permissions needed for Facebook Login and support extra setting values in the case additional permissions are required. <span style="font-size: 8pt;"><a href="../../develop/porting-building-hive/configuration/#config">See more</a></span>
- [Auth v4] Changed not to request the agreement on receiving SMS again without sign-in.
- Stopped supporting Malay and relevant features.
[/markdown]</li></ul>
<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]
- [Provisioning] Changed the way to close your app. If your app is required to close due to a maintenance popup or restriction popup, HIVE SDK used to terminate the application; however, app is closed by sending end event with HIVE SDK v4.9.0. <span style="font-size: 8pt;"><a href="../../develop/authv4/advanced/#app-termination">See more</a></span>
- [Auth v1/Auth v4] Changed to sign in Facebook via Facebook app if the app is installed.
[/markdown]</li></ul>
[markdown]
##### Bug Fixes
[/markdown]<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>[markdown]
- Fixed to deliver the country information of each device in the case of using country key for connecting with HIVE server.
[/markdown]</li></ul>
<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>[markdown]
- [Analytics] Fixed not to miss the userId setting on Singular when signing in with Auth v1 or Auth v4.
- [Auth v1] Fixed not to initialize push settings after SDK initialization.
[/markdown]</li></ul>
<ul class="clList labelList">
  <li><span class="targetLabel iOS">iOS</span>[markdown]
- [Auth v4] Fixed not to simultaneously display a maintenance popup and an access permission notice popup, which is shown up when user plays your game for the first time after installation. 
- [Auth v1/Auth v4] Fixed the veiled part of access permission notice popup.
[/markdown]</li></ul>
