<h3>QQ Android Library</h3>
In the case of using QQ Login for Android among games with Authentication v4, download the following file and install upon consideration of the execution environments..
<ul>
 	<li><a href="http://developers.withhive.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/QQ_Android_Libaray_2.0.zip">Download QQ Android Library</a></li>
 	<li>Installation Path
<ul>
 	<li>Android: (Installed Project)/libs/</li>
 	<li>Unity (Android): (Unity Project)/Assets/Hive_SDK_v4/Plugins/Android/libs/</li>
