<h3>Release Notes</h3>
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Version</strong>: v4.4.1</li>
 	<li><strong>Date</strong>: 2017-Sep-25</li>
</ul>
<h5>New Features</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel iOS">iOS</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[IAP] Supported the feature of  'In-app purchase in App Store' for iOS 11 and later.
<ul>
 	<li>It notifies as UserEngagement event with IapUpdated type.</li>
 	<li>In the case of IAP v2, use IAP.checkPromotePurchase API to check the game PID of the product which got a request for purchase via App Store.</li>
 	<li>In the case of IAP v4, use IAPV4.checkPromotePurchase API to check the game PID of the product which got a request for purchase via App Store.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h5>Changed Features</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[Auth v4] Changed to sign out the IdP account attempted to sign in if the user taps cancellation when account conflicts occur.
<ul>
 	<li>HIVE SDK attempts to sign out conflicted IdP (except Apple Game Center) if user taps cancellation (X) button on the provided UI when using AuthV4.showConflictSelection API.</li>
 	<li>HIVE SDK attempts to sign out conflicted IdP (except Apple Game Center) on customized UI when using AuthV4.resolveConflict API.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel unity">Unity®</span>
<ul>
 	<li>Improved to be compatible with Unity 2017.1.
<ul>
 	<li>'Activity' of HIVE SDK Unity Plugin inherits 'UnityPlayerActivity', so that it works even if the Unity class file is changed.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h5>Bug Fixes</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[Promotion] Fixed UI display error with multi view on Android N (API 24) and later version:
<ul>
 	<li>Wrong size, cropped image wrong format for transverse mode or longitudinal mode.</li>
</ul>
</li>
 	<li>[Social] Fixed HIVE UI display error with multi window on Android N (API 24) and later version.
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Back to game</strong> button on WebView is hidden:</li>
</ul>
</li>
 	<li>[Social] Fixed the wrong settings for <strong>Back to game</strong> button on WebView which should be displayed in Traditional Chinese.</li>
 	<li>[Promotion] Fixed the descender on full banners such as <strong>Don’t show this again today</strong> which seemed to be cropped.</li>
 	<li>[Auth v1] Fixed no response error on the HIVE login screen when user cancelled to sign in Google+ account.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
