<h3>Release Notes</h3>
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Version</strong>: v4.4.0</li>
 	<li><strong>Date</strong>: 2017-Sep-1</li>
</ul>
<h5>New Features</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[IAP v4] Added new HIVE IAP v4 API:
<ul>
 	<li>Guaranteed payment transaction for purchase.</li>
 	<li>Provided visual support about real-time payment state.</li>
 	<li>Collected logs from all payment history through receipt verification.</li>
 	<li>Supported Google Play Store, Apple App Store, One Store, and Lebi.</li>
</ul>
</li>
 	<li>[Auth v4] Added an API to search Facebook friends who play the same game with user when the user synced with Facebook.</li>
 	<li>[Analytics v2] Added to send logs about changes in game server ID if user selects the server after login.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel iOS">iOS</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[Push] Notification Extension Support:
<ul>
 	<li>Supported to send general image (jpg, png), GIF image, and media URL such as mp3, mp4 in HIVE Console &gt; Notification &gt; Push menu (on the device installed iOS 10.2 and later version).</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h5>Changed Features</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[UA] <strong>Changed to set the point at which data can be transferred to be essential in the game. </strong>
<ul>
 	<li>AS-IS: HIVE SDK sends UserAcquisition data to UA server at the receiving time.</li>
 	<li>TO-BE: After HIVE SDK recieves UserAcquistion data, it is sent to UA server when game call UserEngagement.setEngagementReady API (e.g., Implement API after generating data in the game server).</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel iOS">iOS</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[Promotion] Changed to update the result which notifies whether or not the Offerwall is available by using Promotion.getOfferwallState API at the same point of offerwall for Android:
<ul>
 	<li>AS-IS: When succeeded to sign in.</li>
 	<li>TO-BE: When initializing HIVE module, or exposing offerwall pages.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h5>Bug Fixes</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[Push] Fixed the crashes when devices with Android N (7.0) and later receive push notifications after Background Service Policy updated:
<ul>
 	<li>Occurrence depends on the device type in the case Android BuildTarget is 24 and later.</li>
</ul>
</li>
 	<li>Fixed the crashes from displaying UI generated by HIVE SDK and executing games through push notifications in the case HIVE SDK v4.2.6 or v4.3.0 and later version is installed.</li>
 	<li>Fixed the crashes at the time of initializing push notification service in HIVE SDK since network environment or Google Play Services issues occur with earlier than HIVE SDK v4.3.0.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel iOS">iOS</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[UA] Fixed to collect cookies from safari on the devices with iOS 10 and later.</li>
 	<li>[Push] Fixed to expose the Title value input by using Local Push.
<ul>
 	<li>The feature of Title exposure is available for iOS 8.2 and later.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
