<h3 id="release-notes">Release Notes</h3>
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Version</strong>: 4.3.0</li>
 	<li><strong>Date</strong>: 2017-Jun-29</li>
</ul>
<h5>New Features</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>
<ul>
 	<li>[AuthV4] New Authentication System API:
<ul>
 	<li>Integrated API system is now available to authenticate through diverse Identity Providers.</li>
 	<li>Added new feature to support authentication available even when error occurs.</li>
</ul>
</li>
 	<li>[UserEngagement] Improved as an independent system.</li>
 	<li>Applied common identifier.</li>
 	<li>Updated multi-language.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h5>Changed Features</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>
<ul>
 	<li>Third-party Marketing Tracking Analytics Library Update:
<ul>
 	<li>Tune (Android) 4.10.1, Tune (iOS) 4.12.4.</li>
 	<li>Adjust (Android, iOS) 4.11.0.</li>
</ul>
</li>
 	<li>[IAP] Improved to cache Shop data by LocationCode.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h5>Bug Fixes</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel android">Android</span>
<ul>
 	<li>Fixed not to send the Referrer value, delivered by the first execution after installation, to Sandbox server.</li>
 	<li>Fixed to move to the market when HiveSocial opens other apps not installed.</li>
 	<li>[Analytics] Improved to deliver user ID (vid) when sending general events as well as Tune sale data.</li>
 	<li>Fixed to unlock the status of contacts for sync.</li>
 	<li>[Promotion] Fixed the layout of full banner.</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul class="clList labelList">
