 	<li>Updated Facebook SDK from v4.13.1 to v4.18.0.</li>
 	<li>Updated Google Play Services Games from v9.2.1 to v10.0.1+.</li>
 	<li>Added the API to share text or media with other apps.
<ul>
 	<li>Use this feature to send recommendation messages for the game in HIVE User Acquisition program and other use.</li>
 	<li>Text sharing: PlatformHelper.shareText()</li>
 	<li>Media sharing: PlatformHelper.shareMedia()</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
 	<li>Added the API to return HIVE Profile as vid lists.
<ul>
 	<li>SociHive.getProfiles(vidList[], Callback)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
 	<li>Added the API to return login status with Facebook account.
<ul>
 	<li>Distinguished the login status by the existence of Facebook AccessToken.</li>
 	<li>boolean SocialFacebook.isLogin()</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h5>Changed Features</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>
<ul>
 	<li>Added the data of products in a series in the product information of HIVE IAP v2.</li>
 	<li>Added the device model field in the payment log of HIVE IAP v2.</li>
 	<li>Updated result callback of purchase, re-payment in HIVE IAP v2:
<ul>
 	<li>Return the purchase and transaction ID of the successful purchase.
onIAPPurchase(ResultAPI result, Product product, String iapTransactionId)</li>
 	<li>Return the purchase and transaction ID of the successful re-payment.
onIAPRestore(ResultAPI result, Product[] product, String[] iapTransactionId)</li>
</ul>
</li>
 	<li>Changed the actions of User Engagement-related features:
<ul>
 	<li>Changed to configure the starting time of Engagement Event feature by API.
boolean Auth.setEngagementReady(boolean isReady)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h5>Bug Fixes</h5>
<ul class="clList labelList">
 	<li><span class="targetLabel common">All</span>
